  "description": "A woman stands on a grassy hill overlooking a valley and distant ocean. She is dressed in a light-colored, possibly linen, shirt, and vibrant orange pants. A patterned orange and yellow scarf is draped around her shoulders. The hillside is covered in dry, golden grass. In the background, a dense forest of coniferous trees transitions into a blurred view of a valley with hints of a blue ocean. The sky is a soft gradient of blue and pale orange, suggesting late afternoon or early evening light. The woman is smiling and looking directly at the camera, with a relaxed and content expression.",
